<DOCNO>
WSJ900725-0091
</DOCNO>
<DOCID>
900725-0091.
</DOCID>
<HL>
   Who's News:
   Hadco Corp.
</HL>
<DATE>
07/25/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B6
</SO>
<CO>
   HDCO WNEWS
</CO>
<LP>
   HADCO Corp. (Salem, N.H.) -- Patrick Sweeney, vice
president and chief financial officer, was named to the new
post of chief operating officer of this maker of printed
circuit boards.
</LP>
